"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1930652-Olympics-flash-boobs-tennis-TV\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Olympicsviewers could not believe what they were watching when tuned into a tennis match between world No.1 Iga Swiatek and American star Danielle Collins.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 110, \"end\": 113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8530684712089063e-16, \"text\": \"Iga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\"}, {\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\", \"score\": 0.9998796750583584, \"rank\": 0.00012033942156124681, \"text\": \"American star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\"}, {\"begin\": 140, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Collins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Danielle Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Collins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swiatek eventually won after Collins retired through injury in the third set, but during a break in play the TV cameras turned to spectators who had started a Mexican wave.\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 188, \"end\": 195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\", \"score\": 0.9970171999790807, \"rank\": 0.002991723552296927, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\"}, {\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wave_(audience)\", \"score\": 0.9999990027015854, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mexican wave\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wave_(audience)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wave_(audience)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tradition often takes place when fans are bored of the action, coming after a lull in play, but as the cameras focused on three people - a man, woman and child - jaws dropped when that woman lifted up her shirt and flashed the audience.\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans were shocked as the woman raised her top to reveal a bikini underneath, and bizarrely sat in the very next seat to a child who was enjoying the tennis on offer.\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All three smiled and waved to the camera before the flashing, with cameras quickly panning away from the lewd act in order to avoid complaints from viewers.\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When play resumed, Swiatek took the victory after time was called on the match while she led 4-1 in the deciding set, though the contest turned sour whenshe was described as \\\"fake\\\" by her opponentin their conversation at the net.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"I told Iga she did not have to be insincere about, you know, my injury,\\\" Collins recalled.\", \"from\": 1400, \